<li><a href="http://www.morion.com/morion/wood/english/eng_nacken_stagnelius.html" class="external text" title="http://www.morion.com/morion/wood/english/eng_nacken_stagnelius.html" rel="nofollow">The Watersprite</a>, an amateur translation (no rhyme, no meter) of Stagnelius's poem.</li>
<li><a href="http://www.isle-of-man.com/manxnotebook/fulltext/scrap1/ch04_ln.htm" class="external text" title="http://www.isle-of-man.com/manxnotebook/fulltext/scrap1/ch04_ln.htm" rel="nofollow">Manxnotebook</a></li>
<li><a href="http://www.sacred-texts.com/neu/celt/tfm/tfm056.htm" class="external text" title="http://www.sacred-texts.com/neu/celt/tfm/tfm056.htm" rel="nofollow">Sacred-Texts.com</a></li>
<li><a href="http://www.ststp.com/Archives/Scandinavian/Folklore/" class="external text" title="http://www.ststp.com/Archives/Scandinavian/Folklore/" rel="nofollow">Scandinavian Folklore</a></li>
</ul>
